        public boolean isAutoCommitByDefault()
        Description copied from class: ParameterPanel

      • updateParameter

        public void updateParameter(java.lang.String parName,
                   java.lang.String value)
        Sets the parameter in the unit identified by parName to the given value. This function basically calls the setParameter function within the unit and notifies parameter listeners that there has been a change.
